RegTreeView Description
RegTreeView is a simple Registry view using WPF.


A bit about RegTreeView

I was looking on the web for a simple Windows Registry WPF viewer that made use of HierarchicalDataTemplates, but couldn't find one. So I wote my own.



Its a bit rough around the edges, but its a work in progress. You may find it of use, so please download the source code.
